Title: Aztec Secret indian healing clay deep pore cleansing(450 ml)
Description: How Aztec secret works Indian healing clay clays have been used for centuries to beautify and refresh when used as a facial mask. Cleopatra used clay from the Nile River and the Arabian Desert over 1800 years ago, as part of her beauty ritual. German and roman spas have been using clay packs and treatments in the spas they built 4,000 years ago. Many of these spas still exist and use clay even today. Pliney the elder devoted an entire chapter of his natural history" to the many uses of clay for pimples, black heads and skin tightening. Many famous naturopaths, such as kuhn, just and kneipp have contributed to the revival of the uses of clay through their natural treatments for arthritus and skin ailments. Aztec Indian healing clay a brief history - the world's most powerful facial the use of clay with apple cider vinegar can be dated back to the southern French priest of the16th century, kneipp, and his natural treatments using clay packs and poultices. Throughout history the use of clay, specifically green clay or bentonite, is well documented. To learn more about clay, look for "our earth our cure" by Raymond Dexteit, translated by Michel Abehsera in your local health food store or book store. Aztec secret Indian healing clay is bentonite clay from Death Valley, California, where it is sun- dried for up to six months in temperatures that sometimes reach 134 degrees. Facials, acne, body wraps, clay baths, foot soaks, chilled clay for knee packs and insect bites. Enjoy the benefits of clay in your own home. Beautify and refresh.

Title: Skintruth Revitalising Hand Soak
Description: A soothing soak can relieve and energize your hands instantly and help you get back to your daily chores with a new vigor or help you sleep comfortably at night. Skintruth has come up with their Revitalizing Hand Soak to help you pamper your dainty hands in a luxurious invigorating bath. This Revitalizing Hand Soak can be used before manicure treatments to cleanse and prepare them for further treatment. It can also be used on its own to help you relax and to soothe the aching and tired muscles of your hands. The active ingredients in this Hand Soak from Skintruth are neroli and rosemary. Neroli oil is extensively used in aromatherapies to help in uplifting and restoring the skin’s natural texture and softness. Cleansing and toning properties of the neroli oil will help in keeping your hands clean and healthy. The antioxidants present in rosemary will aid in protecting the skin against the harmful effects of free radicals. It invigorates and refreshes the skin with its moisturizing and astringent properties. You can use this Revitalizing Hand Soak from Skintruth to revive your hands after a day’s tiring work or just to give your hands the extra care they need. This can also be used to prep your hands before manicure. Useful tips: • Clean your hands with a mild soap and water. • Pat dry your hands. • Add adequate amount of the Revitalizing Hand Soak from Skintruth to a tub of warm water. Immerse your hands in the warm water and relax. • Keep your hands immersed for at least five minutes to reveal soft, clean and sweet smelling hands.

Description: Playboy’s fragrance collection for men, dedicated to the world capitals, expands with the new edition London. Unexpected and decadent, the established house of Playboy presents New York Deo Spray epitomizing the hep and happening New Yorker who wins wars with his lethal charisma. The mass premium deodorant unleashes the right attitude within him to conquer the sparkling city and makes him hot commodity in all the penthouse parties. The dynamic deodorant spray encapsulates the irreverent cosmopolitan style of the city. The woody, earthy base notes of musk, vanilla, tonka and georgywood add sensuous tones for a striking signature that's as dynamic and exciting as its inspiration.

Tea tree oil is an important addition to your home medicine cabinet and first aid kit due to its fast and effective healing capabilities.Tea Tree Oil has shown a high degree of efficacy in clearing and promoting healthy nails. Title: Indus Valley 100% Botanical Natural Heathier Hair Color(Flame Red)
Description: Indus valley 100% Botanical hair color gives Colour & Care together. Indus Valley Botanical Hair colour is the blend of Certified Organic Herbs without a trace of chemical. It contains Manjistha (Indian Madder) roots, Chemomila flowers, Henna & Indigo to produce variety of colours from Black to Browns to Blondes, totalling 12 in nos. It also contains Cassia (Colourless Henna), Chemomila flowers, Methi (Fenugreek)  which helps in preventing Pre Mature Greying. Blend of Amla, Fenugreek & Cassia prevents Hair Loss & assists in optimising Hair Growth. Brahmi, Henna & Chemomile are known antidandruff herbs which helps in reducing split end hair.How to use:Before applying the colour, shampoo your hair, rinse it well and dry it. Each box of 100% Botanical hair colour contains 2 packets for one to two application, depending on your hair length . Boil 3 cups of pure water. Empty out the packet of 100% Botanical hair colour in a non-metallic (glass or plastic) mixing bowl. Pour one/cup of boiled water into the powder, stirring continuously with a non metallic spoon or spatula to break the lumps. Add enough of the boiled water to obtain a honey like consistency of the paste. After that keep the mixture for 1-2 minutes for thicken and stabilize. Apply mixture at the crown of the head, coating all strands with the help of supplied brush or Fingers. Leave mixture on your head for 30-45 minutes.
